Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.42,0:00:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个视频里，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们开始在实践中应用盒子模型
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是边距和填充。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们从填充和一个伟大的候选人开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,添加一些填充是这里的标题元素，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它具有这种背景颜色。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一个有背景颜色的元素，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是可以使用一些填充来创造一些空间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在元素的内容和外部之间。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为记住填充基本上只是空间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是元素的内部。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这个元素被称为主标题，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们在这里的某个地方有它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实在这里。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在实际上，我想做的是把这段代码放到这里，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是用于这些盒子的，并将其放在顶部。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我喜欢有，像这些大的水平盒子，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以包含多个子元素的盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或更多在顶部。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.97,0:01:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这里的这个标题是这些大盒子中的第一个。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我会把它放在身体后面。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.19,0:01:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在让我们从添加一些填充开始。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.61,0:01:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们使用填充，一个属性，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们需要指定一些长度。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们使用 20 像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以像素与我们使用的单位完全相同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用于边框宽度，也用于字体大小。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么让我们看看它是什么样子的。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上，我们现在得到了一些新的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在内容之间，所以在这一切之间，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然还有元素的外部。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在看起来这里的空间和这里一样。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以它是 20 像素，但是这里有更多的空间。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，让我们右键单击此元素并检查。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在这里你看到了原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以当我们将鼠标悬停在一个元素上时，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们实际上得到了那个元素的边距。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那个红色或橙色的覆盖层。现在对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在标题本身，你看到那里的绿色空间，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是填充。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你会看到事实上，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填充物在盒子周围
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或在盒子内部的所有周围
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且到处都是20像素。\N00:02:39,130​​ --> 00:02:39,963\N好的。\N\N50
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们稍后会在这里修复这个边距
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时，一切都会变得有意义。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在实际上在风格上，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以看到盒子模型。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在这里我们确实看到了，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:03:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都有 20 的填充，所以在所有四个边上。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这里的这个其实就是宽度和高度，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是填充，然后是边框，然后是边距。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以对于每个元素，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个完整的盒子模型表示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在开发工具中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多时候这非常有帮助。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们现在肯定会使用它，稍后再使用。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这里的填充确实创建了相同的填充
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在盒子的所有四个侧面。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果我们想创建不同的填充
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不同的方面，我们也可以很容易地做到这一点。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以假设我们想要一个不同的填充
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在左边和右边。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们可以说，例如，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右各 40 像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这实际上是一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与边界一样。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以记住边界，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:04:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有边框顶部、边框底部、左侧和右侧。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在，确实，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左侧的空间比
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在底部。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右边也是一样，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我们无法从内容上真正看到它，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们可以使用开发工具在这里看到它。对？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你在右边看到，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在左边有 40、40 个，然后在顶部和底部有 20 个。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在，我们实际上可以用更好的方式来写这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次使用一种叫做速记的东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，当我们指定多个值时，总是简写
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是一处房产。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以对于填充，我们可以做的是，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是仅仅指定一个值，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在所有四个站点上都是相同的，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以指定两个值。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们这样做，那么第一个值将是填充
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在顶部和底部。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:05:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二个值将在左侧填充
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和右侧。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要达到和以前一样的结果，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会说 20 像素和 40 像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果我们现在在这里删除这句话，像这样，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用注释，那么我们的结果还是一样的。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们用这个速记在顶部和底部加20，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和 40 左右。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们就不必写所有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有不同的代码行。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以一口气做完。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来，让我们玩一点边距。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请记住，边距基本上是空格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元素之间。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在让我们在 LI 元素之间添加一些空间。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这里的这些，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到他们非常接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且看起来不太好。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我们可以在底部添加一些边距
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些元素中的每一个。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这里的某个地方，一定有，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以已经有了LI，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们不需要一遍又一遍地选择它。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是写在这里，在相同的规则内。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们说底部的边距，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10 像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在看起来确实好多了，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们在这里选择它。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得到 10 个像素
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他们每个人的边缘底部。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚动到最后一个，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在我想给你看一些东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以通常在最后一个列表项中，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不想有任何空间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们实际上只想要项目之间的空间，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是在项目的末尾。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:07:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以再一次，少一个不应该有任何空间。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们为此使用一个技巧，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实际上是我们之前学到的东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们可以说LI，然后是last-child。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在这里，我们基本上重置了我们刚刚所做的。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们说边距底部并将其设置为零。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当我们使用零时，我们不指定任何单位。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们只说零，然后它将覆盖它。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们以前在这里的空间应该消失了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你会看到这个没有边距，但是在它之前的那个，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,底部确实有这 10 个像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错，很美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在将继续增加越来越多的利润
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和填充到我们所有的元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在我们这样做之前，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们实际上应该做一些称为全局重置的事情。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，如果您在这里查看我们的页面，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们关闭它，然后你会注意到，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里其实已经有很多空间了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这里的 H2 元素周围有空间，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段落之间，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样在这里，正如我们在使用开发工具之前所看到的，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个H1的顶部和底部有很多余量。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并拥有所有这些默认边距和填充，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我们很难为页面设置样式。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们要做的是重置所有这些边距
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和填充，基本上将它们设置为零。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么您认为我们如何做到这一点？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我们应该使用继承吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你认为margin和padding会被继承吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一个元素到另一个元素？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，让我们测试并将边距设置为零。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么让我们看看。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，实际上确实发生了一些变化。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以身体失去了它所拥有的边缘。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在一切都像是粘在了这里的边界上。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以到视口的边界，所以浏览器本身，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并非所有元素都失去了边距，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这不是真正要走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为边距不是与文本相关的属性，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此它不是可以继承的属性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从父元素到子元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反，如果我们想要应用边距
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到每一个元素，然后为此，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以使用通用选择器。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以边距设置为零，填充设置为零。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这正是我们正在寻找的结果。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在所有的默认空间都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:10:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以随意格式化我们的页面。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里做这样的事情，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这种全局重置非常普遍。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这通常是我做的第一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当我开始任何新项目时。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要记住，这里的边距和填充
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常容易被覆盖。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以所有其他选择器实际上都会覆盖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个通用选择器。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上，我们可以在主标题中看到，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们确实指定了一些填充，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以当然它在这里仍然可见。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以再一次，这个类选择器在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具有比全局选择器更高的优先级。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用更多的技术术语来说，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们说通用选择器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特异性为零，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 VS 代码在此工具提示中向我们展示的内容。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而另一方面，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:11:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的这个选择器确实在这些地方之一。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这个更具体。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它具有更高的优先级，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此填充确实被应用。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此列表中也是如此。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在这里我们也应该已经有了 10 个像素
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之前指定的。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有了这个重置，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在添加我们的自定义空间非常容易
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并让这个页面看起来真的很设计。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我们已经到了，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们从 &lt;aside&gt; 开始。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或继续在这里。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为再一次，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是具有背景颜色的元素之一。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以为了创造一些空间，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该使用填充，否则，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的边框真的粘在了内容上。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这不是我们想要的。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:12:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们说填充50像素的顶部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且填充底部也是 50 像素，
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们给它一个保存，看起来好多了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在我们把左边和右边都设为零，
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们稍后会解决这个问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们怎么能在这里写这个，
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上以更好的方式？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，我希望你猜到了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案是使用速记。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只需在顶部和底部填充，
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 50 像素的第一个值
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二个值是我们想要零的左右。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在，就是这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把这个拿出来，
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给它一个保存，它看起来仍然一样。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在，好吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在让我们上到页面顶部。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在这里，我们可能需要一些空间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:13:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个标题和这个 H2 元素之间，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这看起来很糟糕。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们需要在这个元素之外有一些空间。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在这两者之间，为此，
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以在下方使用边距底部，
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上这个标题元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们来到我们的主要标题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设边缘底部为 60 像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而事实上，
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很常见，主要使用底部的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了创造垂直空间。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要坚持到任何一个边距顶部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或总是边缘底部。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以其中一个很好，
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最好不要总是在需要时混合它们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在元素之间创建空间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就个人而言，我真的很喜欢使用margin bottom。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来，这样做很有意义。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，让我们继续。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:14:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许现在在这个 H2 下方添加一些空间。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以H2就在这里。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们再说一次底部的边距，
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里我们只使用 30 个像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样，这里的这些值是非常随机的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍后我们将使用一个系统来自动，
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上为我们创造了这些价值。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来，让我们在这部分之间创建一些空间。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以基本上是这张图片，然后是其余的内容。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们看一下我们的标记，
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部分，所以这张图片，这个作者，
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的另一个图像是这个标题。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，让我们在此标题的底部添加一些边距。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我给它起了另一个名字。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这个是主要的标题。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们在这里称它为帖子标题。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们复制到这里，
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在这里，
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后边距底部 40 像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这要好得多。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来，我想考虑段落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为，好吧，现在看起来很乱。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只需在底部添加一些空间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个段落，
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这将使它立即变得更好。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以边距底部，让我们在这里尝试 15 像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上，这已经好多了。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在与这些列表相同。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在在这里，在这个有序列表中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我们这里的无序列表，
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在，实际上数字和要点已经消失了。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我们实际上需要一些空间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在左侧，以便可以显示它们。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们把它们加回来，因为，
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的全局重置，基本上删除了所有这些空间。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们想要无序列表中的那个空间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且也在有序列表中。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们说左边的边距，
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如，
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个 50 像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在你看到了，他们回来了。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一切都向右移动了 50 个像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在是那个，所以数字和项目符号又回来了。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们在底部添加一些空间，
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20 像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在让我们继续讨论 H3。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这就是这里。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以边距底部 20 像素，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了点问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我显然不能拼写margin。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以看起来好多了。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们还需要指定一些距离
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此文本和此标题之间。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在看起来，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两者之间的空间是完全一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不好。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实际上正在这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想给你看一些东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我现在要指定边距顶部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并将其设置为 40 像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。现在效果很好。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，现在让我向您展示一些使用开发工具的东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我正在检查这个元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你看到正好有 20 个像素
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们在底部指定的，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及我们指定到顶部的 40 个像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而，在它之前的这段，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实底部也有边距，
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信，15像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这个，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在这个元素到顶部有 40 像素
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个底部有 15 个像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这两个空间都占据了这个区域，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们可能会直觉地认为，
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个空间确实加起来了。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以基本上，这15个像素将被添加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到来自这里的 40 个像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在 f行动，这不是发生的事情。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们在这里看到事实上，
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个元素之间的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只有40像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不是 55 像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种现象被称为边缘收缩。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以基本上，
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们有两个占据相同空间的边距时，
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:19:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有其中一个在页面上实际可见。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这通常是两者中较大的一个。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如，
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设我们指定了，比如这里的 40 像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们可能会认为，
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实际上是 80 像素，
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以遵循与之前相同的逻辑。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当然它仍然只有 40 像素
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为边距塌陷。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果我们在这里有 100 个像素呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，现在这里的空间实际上是 100 像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以正是你在那里看到的这个橙色空间。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这个现在还有40个，
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个有一百个。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在他们之间的距离还不是140，
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它是&lt;p&gt;底部的这一百个像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这就是我们说话时的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于折叠边距，
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你可能会听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.27,0:20:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦你开始听到人们谈论一些 CSS，
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的怪癖或类似 CSS 内部的奇怪东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，但是，我认为我们基本上已经完成了。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们在这里添加更多空间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这些相关帖子和所有这些内容之间，
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个是文章，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们有文章和&lt;aside&gt;。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们也需要一些空间。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我不认为我是否已经在任何地方选择了这篇文章
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来我没有，
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们把它放在顶部。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我在这里，
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将抓住这个导航并将其也放在顶部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它是那些更大的元素之一。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我喜欢让他们保持在顶部。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然，这篇文章也是如此。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以文章，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一个很好的 60 像素边距底部。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们开始，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样，这是我们的页面讨厌的格式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在边距和填充方面。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只是快速回顾一下，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当您需要元素内部的一些空间时，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是非常有用的，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是当有背景颜色时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或元素上的边框，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你总是使用填充。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了在元素之外创造空间，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者也可以在多个元素之间创建空间，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始终使用边距。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您需要添加垂直空间，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我建议你大部分时间，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持边距底部。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以基本上这就是增加空间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:21:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我们的页面元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在接下来的讲座中，
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.18,0:22:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们还将添加尺寸，例如高度和宽度。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.42,0:00:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In this video,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,let's start applying the box model in practice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and in particular margins and paddings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And let's start with padding and one great candidate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,for adding some padding is this header element here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which has this background color.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So an element which has background color,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,can always use some padding in order to create some space
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,between the content and the outside of an element.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because remember padding is basically just space
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that is inside of the element.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this element is called the main header,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I think we have it somewhere down here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and indeed here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now actually, what I want to do is to take this code here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which is for these boxes and put it a bit more to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I like to have, like these big level boxes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so boxes that contain multiple child elements
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or more at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.97,0:01:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this header here is kind of the first of these big boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so I will put it here right after the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.19,0:01:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now let's start by adding some padding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.61,0:01:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we use the padding, a property,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then we need to specify some length.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's use 20 pixels.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so pixels is exactly the same unit that we also used
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,for the border width, and also for font sizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's see what that looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And indeed, we now got ourselves some new space that is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,between the content, so between all of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and of course the outside of the element.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now it looks like the space here is the same as here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it's 20 pixels, but then here there's a lot more space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's right click here on this element and inspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so here you see the reason for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So when we hover over an element,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we actually get the margin off that element.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so that is that red or that orange overlay. Now right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now the header itself, you see the green space there,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that is the padding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll see that in fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the padding goes all around the box
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or all around the inside of the box
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it is really 20 pixels everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we will fix this margin here in a second
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and by then, everything will make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now actually down here in the styles,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we can see the box model.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so here we see that indeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:03:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there is padding of 20 everywhere, so on all four sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this one here is actually the width and height,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then the padding, then the border and then the margin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So for each element,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there is a complete representation of the box model
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,right here in the dev tools
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and many times this is extremely helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we will use this now for sure, a bit later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now this padding here does create the same padding
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on all four sides of the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if we wanted to create different paddings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on different sides, we can do that also just very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's say we want a different paddings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,at the left and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we can say for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40 pixels on the left and on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so this is in fact exactly the same thing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as with the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So remember with the border,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:04:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we also have border top, border bottom, left, and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now indeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there's a lot more space here on the left side than
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the same here on the right side,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,even though we cannot really see it by the content,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but we can see it here using the dev tools. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you see that here on the right,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we have 40, 40 on the left and then 20 on top and on bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now, we can actually write this in an even better way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,by using something called a shorthand once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So a shorthand is always when we specify multiple values
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,here for one property.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So for padding, what we can do is to,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,instead of just specifying one value,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which will then be the same on all four sites,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we can specify two values.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if we do that, then the first value will be padding
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on the top and bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:05:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the second value will be padding on the left
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and right side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So to achieve the same result as before,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we would say 20 pixels and 40 pixels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so if we now removed this quote here, like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,using a comment, then our result is still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we use this shorthand to add 20 to top and bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and 40 to left and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this way we don't have to write all of these
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,different lines of codes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can just do it all in one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, let's play a little bit with margins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And remember that margins are basically spaces
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,between elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's now add some space between the LI elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So these ones here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you see that they're very close together
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it doesn't look nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And therefore we can add some margin to the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of each of these elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So somewhere down here, there must,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so there is the LI already,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so we don't need to select it over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We just write it here, inside the same rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so let's say margin to the bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10 pixels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so now that does look a lot better, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's select this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And indeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we get 10 pixels
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,at the margin bottom on each of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just scroll to the last one,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because now I want to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So usually in the last list item,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we don't want to have any space
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because we actually only want space between the items,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but not at the end of the items.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:07:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So again, the less one should not have any space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so let's use a trick for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which is actually something that we learned before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we can say LI, and then last-child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then here, we basically reset what we just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we say margin bottom and set it to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And whenever we use zero, we do not specify any unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we just say zero and that will then override it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now that space that we had here before should be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll see this one has no margin, but the one before it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that does have these 10 pixels at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, that's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And we will now keep adding more and more margins
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and paddings to all of our elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But before we do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we should actually do something called a global reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if you take a look at our page here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and let's close this, then you notice that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there are actually already a lot of spaces here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So there's space around this H2 element here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,between the paragraphs,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,also here, as we saw before using the dev tools,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there was a lot of margin on the top and bottom of this H1.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And having all of these default margins and paddings,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,makes it quite hard for us to style our page.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what we want to do is to reset all those margins
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and paddings, and basically set them to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So how do you think we can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we should use inheritance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So do you think that margin and padding get inherited
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,from one element to the other?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's test and set the margin to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And well, something actually did change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So the body lost the margin that it had.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So now everything is really like glued to the border here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So to the border of the viewport, so the browser itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but not all the elements lost its margin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so this is not really the way to go
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because margin is not a property that is related to text,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and therefore it's not a property that gets inherited
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,from parents to child elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Instead if we want the margin to be applied
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to every single element, then for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we can use the universal selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So margin set to zero and padding set to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now this is exactly the result that we were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So now all the default spaces are gone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:10:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we are free to format our page as we wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And doing something like this here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so this kind of global reset is extremely common.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is usually the very first thing that I do
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,whenever I start any new project.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And also keep in mind that, this margin and padding here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are extremely easy to overwrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So every other selector will actually overwrite
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this universal selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And in fact, we can see that right here in the main header,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,where we did specify some padding,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and so of course it is still visible here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So once again, this class selector here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,has a higher priority than the global selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And in more technical terms,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we say that the universal selector
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,has a specificity of zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which is what VS code shows us here, in this tool tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,While on the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:11:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this selector here does have the one in one of these places.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this one is more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It has a higher priority,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and therefore the padding does get applied.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the same is true also right here in this list.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So here we also, already should have the 10 pixels
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that we just specified previously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now with this reset in place,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it is extremely easy to now add our custom spaces
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and to make this page really look designed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And since we're already here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,let's actually start here with the &lt;aside&gt;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or keep going here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this is one of the elements which has a background color.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so therefore in order to create some space,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we should use padding because, otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this border here is really glued to the content.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's not what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:12:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's say padding top of 50 pixels
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and padding bottom of also 50 pixels,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,let's give it a save and that looks a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So for now we're leaving left and right side at zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we will fix that a bit later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So how could we write this here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,actually in a bit better way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I hope you guessed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the answer would be to use the shorthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So just padding at the top and bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which is the first value of 50 pixels
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the second value is left and right where we want zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So take this out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,give it a save and it still does look the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's go up to the top of the page.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now here, we probably need some space
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:13:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,between this header and this H2 element here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this looks very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so we need some space outside of this element here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So between these two, and for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we can use a margin bottom below,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,basically this header element.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's come here to our main header
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and at a margin bottom of let's say, 60 pixels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it is in fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,very common to use mostly space at the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in order to create vertical space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So just a stick to either margin top
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or always margin bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So one of them is fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it's best not to always mix them when you want
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to create space between elements
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and personally, I really like to use margin bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It makes a lot of sense in my mind to do it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay and let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:14:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe add some space now, below this H2.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So H2 is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's say a margin at the bottom, once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and here we just use 30 pixels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And again, these values here are quite random
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and later we will use a system to automatically,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,basically create these values for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next, let's create some space here between this part.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So basically this image and then the rest of the content.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if we take a look at our markup,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that part, so this image, this author,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and this other image here is this header.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's add some margin bottom to this header.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so I'm giving it another name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this one is the main header.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's call this one here, the post header.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's copy that here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,put it here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then margin bottom of 40 pixels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's a lot nicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I want to think about the paragraphs
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because, well, this looks very messy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so just by adding some space to the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of each paragraph,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that will make it a lot better immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So margin bottom, and let's try 15 pixels here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And indeed that is a lot better already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now the same with these lists.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So now here, in this ordered list
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and this unordered list that we have here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,now, actually the numbers and the bullet points are a gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that is because we actually need some space
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on the left side so that they can be shown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's add them back because,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,our global reset, basically removed all those spaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we want that space in the unordered list
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and also in the ordered list.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's say margin on the left side,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a 50 pixel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so now you see that, they are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So everything moved 50 pixels to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so now the one, so the numbers and the bullets are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's also add some space to the bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20 pixels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now let's move on to the H3.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's this one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So margin bottom 20 pixels,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and something is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot spell margin apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that looks a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now we also need to specify some distance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,between this text here and this heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So right now it looks like,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the space between these two is exactly the same
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and that's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm actually doing this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because I want to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm gonna specify the margin top now
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and set it to 40 pixels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Now that works beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, let me now show you something using the dev tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm inspecting this element.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so you see that there is exactly the 20 pixels
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that'd we specified to the bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the 40 pixels that we specified to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, this paragraph that comes before it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,actually also has a margin to the bottom of,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe, 15 pixels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So right now this element here has 40 pixels to the top
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and this one has 15 pixels to the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so both of these spaces occupy this area here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so we might intuitively think that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,these two spaces do get added up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So basically that, these 15 pixels here will get added
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to the 40 pixels that come from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But in fact, that is not what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we see here that in fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the distance between the two elements
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is really just 40 pixels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is not 55 pixels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this phenomena is called collapsing margins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when we have two margins that occupied the same space,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:19:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,only one of them is actually visible on the page.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that is usually the larger of the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,let's say that we specified, like 40 pixels here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then we might've thought that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this was actually 80 pixels here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so following the same logic from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But of course it is still only 40 pixels
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because of the collapsing margins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But what if we had like 100 pixels here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, now the space here would in fact be 100 pixels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So exactly this orange space that you see right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this one now still has its 40,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but this one has a hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so now the space between them is still not 140,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it's these hundred pixels of the bottom of the &lt;p&gt;.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what we mean when we talk
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,about collapsing margins,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which is something that you might hear
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.27,0:20:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,once you start hearing people talking about some CSS,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,weird quirks or like weird stuff that is inside of CSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And, but this, I think we are basically almost done already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just add some more space here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,between these related posts and all this content here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which is the article, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we have article and the &lt;aside&gt;.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we need some space there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't think if I already selected the article anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it looks like I didn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so let's put that at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And since I'm here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will grab this nav and put it also at the top
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because it's one of those bigger elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I like to keep them at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And of course the same goes for the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So article,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and a nice margin bottom of 60 pixel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And here we go,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that's it, that's our page nasty formatted
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in terms of margins and paddings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So just to quickly recap,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,whenever you need some space inside of an element,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which is very useful,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,mostly when there is a background color
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or a border on the element,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then you always use padding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in order to create space outside of an element,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or also to create space between multiple elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,always use margin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And in case that you need to add vertical space,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then I advise you to most of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,stick to margin bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so basically that's it about adding space
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:21:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to our page elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And in the next lecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.18,0:22:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we will then also add dimensions, so height and width.